<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Siva Krishna - CI/CD with Jenkins</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #ee7752, #e73c7e, #23a6d5, #23d5ab);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 15s ease infinite;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        @keyframes gradientBG {
            0% {background-position: 0% 50%;}
            50% {background-position: 100% 50%;}
            100% {background-position: 0% 50%;}
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 56px;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px #ffd700;
            color: #fff700;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #ffccff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #ff66ff;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .emoji {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="emoji">✨🚀👨‍💻🎯</div>
    <h1>Siva Krishna</h1>
    <h2>CI/CD Setup Success with Jenkins Freestyle ✅</h2>
    <p>
        Achieved seamless integration and delivery using GitHub, Maven, Jenkins, SonarQube, Nexus, and Tomcat.<br>
        Automated workflows = Faster delivery + Higher quality! 🔧💻🔥
    </p>
    <div class="footer">🚀 Proudly built using DevOps tools</div>
</body>
</html>
